{"tid":774690,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布苟姑娘既貞操會喺今年度10月19日終結","createTime":"2018-08-10T13:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T13:43:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43e84c75e7a3716adb7791ce4ab74aa685625a82","tid":774690,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:43:33.000Z","msg":"【今日直擊】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">苟芸慧今日出席香水展時透露將於10月19日出嫁，</span></span>婚禮地點為上水雙魚河私人會所，婚宴就會分兩日舉行，一日供雙方親戚及長輩參加，另一場就邀請同事及朋友出席。她表示王君馨、岑麗香已答應做姊妹，懷有身孕的李亞男要視乎情況，屆時剛生完第二胎不久的鍾嘉欣就無奈缺席。苟芸慧說︰「陸漢洋要求取消玩新郎環節，說直接向兄弟姊妹派利市。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/214244_b3099e5df8626af0ded9263c058fd595.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F214244_b3099e5df8626af0ded9263c058fd595.png&h=95bb72f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1533901589481&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1533901589481%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180810&d=idlRQUqkF3qAdBQ7IAyxfS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=df2453cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1533901589481%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180810&h=cdd4a178\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1533901589481&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180810</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}